In [7]:
AI_tune <- nearest_neighbor(weight_func = "rectangular", neighbors = tune()) |>
    set_engine("kknn") |>
    set_mode("classification")
AI_vfold <- vfold_cv(train, v = 5, strata = churn) 
k = tibble(neighbors = seq(from = 1, to = 50, by = 1))
AI_test_k <- workflow() |>
    add_recipe(rec) |>
    add_model(AI_tune) |>
    tune_grid(resamples = AI_vfold, grid = k) |>
    collect_metrics() |>
    filter(.metric == "accuracy")

In [9]:
kknn_model <- nearest_neighbor(weight_func = "rectangular", neighbors = 42) |>
    set_engine("kknn") |>
    set_mode("classification")

kknn_fit <- workflow() |>
    add_recipe(rec) |>
    add_model(kknn_model) |>
    fit(train)

kknn_predictions <- kknn_fit |>
    predict(test) |>
    bind_cols(test) |>
    mutate(pred = if_else(.pred_class == "Yes", 1, 0)) |> 
    mutate(churn = if_else(Customer_Churn == 0, "No", "Yes")) |>
    mutate(churn = as.factor(churn))

kknn_results <- kknn_predictions |>
    metrics(truth = churn, estimate = .pred_class) 
kknn_results

In [10]:
set.seed(1000)

fold <- trainControl(method = "cv",  
                     number = 5, 
                     verboseIter = TRUE)  

rf_model <- train(as.factor(Customer_Churn) ~  AI_Interaction_Level + Change_in_Usage_Patterns + Satisfaction_with_AI_Services,          # Formula for the model
                  data = train,         
                  method = "rf",       
                  trControl = fold) 
rf_predictions <- predict(rf_model, newdata = test) |>
    bind_cols(test) |>
    mutate(pred = ...1) |>
    select(-...1)

rf_results <- rf_predictions |>
    summarize(n = sum(Customer_Churn == pred)) |>
    summarize(accuracy = n / 1250)
rf_results

svm_model <- svm(as.factor(Customer_Churn) ~ AI_Interaction_Level + Change_in_Usage_Patterns + Satisfaction_with_AI_Services, data = train, kernel = "radial")

    bind_cols(test) |>
    mutate(pred = ...1) |>
    select(-...1)

svm_results <- svm_predictions |>
    summarize(n = sum(Customer_Churn == pred)) |>
    summarize(accuracy = n / 1250)

In [12]:
AI_predictions <- test |>
    bind_cols(kknn_predictions$pred) |>
    bind_cols(rf_predictions$pred) |>
    bind_cols(svm_predictions$pred) |>
    mutate(kknn_pred = ...11,
           rf_pred = ...12,
           svm_pred = ...13) |>
    select(-...11, -...12, -...13) |>
    select(ID, Customer_Churn, kknn_pred, rf_pred, svm_pred)

AI_predictions <- AI_predictions |>
    mutate(kknn_pred = as.numeric(kknn_pred),
           rf_pred = as.numeric(rf_pred) - 1,
           svm_pred = as.numeric(svm_pred) - 1,
           final_pred = (kknn_pred + svm_pred + rf_pred)/3) |>
    mutate(final_pred = if_else(final_pred > 0.5, 1, 0)) |>
    summarize(accuracy = sum(final_pred == Customer_Churn)/1250)

stacked_features <- data.frame(kknn_predictions, rf_predictions, svm_predictions)

top_model <- randomForest(as.factor(Customer_Churn) ~ pred + pred.1 + pred.2, data = stacked_features)
new_predictions <- predict(top_model, stacked_features) |>
    bind_cols(test) |>
    mutate(pred = ...1)

final <- new_predictions |>
    select(ID, pred)

new_predictions_accuracy <- new_predictions |>
    summarize(accuracy = sum(pred == Customer_Churn)/1250)
